            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288091</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Samsung 近年趋向愈来愈早推出旗下年度首部旗舰手机，由二月底到二月初，去到今年更早至一月底就发布新一代的 Galaxy S25 系列。早前 Edward 就有幸提早试玩 3 部全新 Galaxy S25 系列的新机，现在就让笔者与 unwire.hk 读者们分享一下这部全新旗舰，尤其是 S25 Ultra 的初步体验感受吧。</p><h2>完整现场评测影片</h2><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_37185"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bUmxSmrvRHI?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><h2>S25 Ultra 设计向 S25 / S25+ 靠拢感觉更「一家人」</h2><p>今代 Samsung 推出的全新 Galaxy S25 系列，与上代一样依然设有 Galaxy S25、Galaxy S25+ 及 Galaxy S25 Ultra，早前传闻的 Galaxy S25 Slim 就暂时仍未见到实机。至于设计方面，整个 S25 系列新机与上代分别不算太大，机面及机背依然采用强化玻璃制造，不过玻璃就用上较新的康宁 Gorilla Glass Victus 2，对机身耐磨度及耐用性有更佳效果。荧幕方面，S25、S25+ 及 S25 Ultra 就分别配置了 6.2 吋、6.7 吋及 6.9 吋荧幕，由此可见前两者荧幕未有增大，但 S25 Ultra 就比上代加大了 0.1 吋。还有一点大家可以留意到，就是今代 S25 Ultra 在机身设计上感觉进一步向 S25 / S25+ 靠拢，相比上代 S24 Ultra 采用更方角的设计，今代 S25 Ultra 角位改回圆角风格，虽然与 S25 / S25+ 相比依然较为方角，但相比上代 S24 Ultra 肯定是较圆角，笔者上手感觉没有了上代机角的「刺手掌」手感，握在手上使用手感更加理想。另外，今代似乎机身更薄更轻，尤其是 S25 Ultra 的体验更是明显，加上 S25 Ultra 的荧幕边框比上代更窄，因此今代虽然荧幕增大了 0.1 吋，但机身阔度没有明显扩阔，所以单手操控仍然问题不大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288096" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08398-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08398-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08398.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新一代的 Samsung Galaxy S25 系列旗舰手机刚刚推出，依然设有三部机款，分别是 Galaxy S25（左）、Galaxy S25+（上）及 Galaxy S25 Ultra（右）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288097" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08400-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08400-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08400.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288098" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08407-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08407-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08407.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲设计方面，Galaxy S25（左）、Galaxy S25+（中）及 Galaxy S25 Ultra（右）的荧幕及机背同样采用强化玻璃保护，采用的是较新的 Corning Gorilla Glass Victus 2。另外，荧幕尺寸分别为 6.2 吋、6.7 吋及 6.9 吋，当中 S25 Ultra 采用较幼荧幕边框，因此可以保有与上代相近尺寸同时，荧幕比上代大了 0.1 吋。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288099" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08401-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08401-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08401.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身设计风格上，Galaxy S25 及 S25+ 大致与上代差不多，而 S25 Ultra 就比上代采用相对较圆角的设计，风格上向 S25 及 S25+ 靠拢，感觉更像「一家人」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288100" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08404-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08404-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08404.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身边框方面，S25 及 S25+ 依然用上铝金属物料，而 S25 Ultra 就仍然用上钛金属物料。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288101" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08507-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08507-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08507.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288102" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08500-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08500-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08500.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288103" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08495-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08495-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08495.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲手感方面，由于三机设计趋于一统，所以手感亦十分相似，当然机身较细的 Galaxy S25（第一张）及 S25+（第二张）在单手操控上最为舒服，而 S25 Ultra（第三张）虽然机身较大，但今代比上代更轻薄，所以单手操控仍没有大问题。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288104" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08503-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08503-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08503.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288105" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08498-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08498-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08498.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288106" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08493-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08493-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08493.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Galaxy S25（第一张）、Galaxy S25+（第二张）及 Galaxy S25 Ultra（第三张）在单手握机操控及打字也没有太大问题。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08484-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08484-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/dsc08484.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲作业系统方面，依然用上以 Android 15 为基础而设计的 OneUI 7.0 作业系统。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
